{"tid":828294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国已經有有效的方法令廠家不會撤走, 美國要輸了","createTime":"2018-09-19T14:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T14:41:35.000Z","uid":76310,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"efa45abe84371394beefbf3077926f40d5173be4","tid":828294,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q4s7o9EmLJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ4s7o9EmLJA&d=CcPOoo3GE3umE%2F%2BZ%2BO3uGsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a0d5c8b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q4s7o9EmLJA</a><br />\n馬雲：貿易戰或持續20年，港商代工廠關閉，為防止跑路，已經全部被監控<br />\n<br />\n中国：當年国家提供那麼多優惠政策，給了你們做廠這麼多好處，現在国家有小小危機，做廠的不能撤走<br />\n<br />\n當年国家提供廉價土地，廉價水電，稅務優惠，廉價工人，還提供中国既頂尖美女<br />\n国家把你們這班廠商養得肚滿腸肥，富可敵国，家財萬貫，個個都是富豪<br />\n<br />\n做廠不能走，要回饋国家，思念當日国家的恩情和恩𧶽<br />\n要走就賠番當日所有賺既錢出來，這些錢都是国家當日賜予給你們的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7951ebcb43565c98684af248e54f4fde81881e71","tid":828294,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e119d89f09164d8baa414018e17727a3805d834e","tid":828294,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a1f5709ab466877e56bd13de0be14597a130e75","tid":828294,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"唔做都唔得，慘過做雞"},{"pid":"d6a48068c2336a35a32315e851632376c1a63f13","tid":828294,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:29:37.000Z","msg":"北京懼港商撤離 安撫監視防走佬<br />\n加上貿易戰下，中共經濟吃緊，紛紛拿私企開刀。今年10月1日推行新稅法，課稅起徵點提高到每月5,000元（人民幣，下同），且個人與個體工商戶等經營所得，也將按照新的稅率表計稅。他直言，雙重打擊下，「很多公司都頂不住」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，兩年前東莞有近8萬間港資廠，今年只剩約2.5萬間。<br />\n<br />\n不過，對於貿易戰下的外資撤離潮，據稱中共嚴密封鎖相關消息，包括早前下達禁令，貿易戰不得上熱點頭條等。傑斯指，中共很懼怕外資撤離，擔心引發骨牌效應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">據他透露，這兩三個星期，很多美國公司都要求搬廠，但中共當局就採取所謂的維穩措施，如針對二、三百人規模以上的企業，東莞市、鎮政府就派人「安撫」，找工廠主管談話，又墊支工人欠薪，「怕你走佬」。同時中共還監視他們，「將你的行蹤盯實」，變成接美國單的港商左右為難，壓力很大。</span><br />\n<br />\n對於未來港商前景，他直言感到悲觀，「現環境一年差過一年，今年最差，幾乎所有代工廠都要關閉。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2018-09-19/68078600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2018-09-19%2F68078600&d=CcPOoo3GE3umE%2F%2BZ%2BO3uGsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=fc4eedb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2018-09-19/68078600</a>"},{"pid":"b27bd91ad72f292fdbf6a3e1438db294d4d2bcfd","tid":828294,"uid":182475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"既強姦，又焗賭。"},{"pid":"5b78a5e421a48bfd5fc84511f005de20e0d0636d","tid":828294,"uid":146535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0a1f5709ab466877e56bd13de0be14597a130e75","tid":828294,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"唔做都唔得，慘過做雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"中共食神嚟，你邊估得到佢<br />\n收左利是連煙頭都要食<br />\n大聲叫又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畀著以前唔好老脾一腳踢你落海<br />\n再掛喺度鞭屍<br />\n佢好人嚟架嘛"},{"pid":"1473254035c1653e65f13bf0da23a774d7df409c","tid":828294,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"真係值錢嗰啲係外資，支那夠膽唔俾走？<br />\n港商就算啦，愛國付出下有咩所謂"},{"pid":"0e8434e42d9b2c8d6664594baf0f7f4f196a71a4","tid":828294,"uid":96743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:41:35.000Z","msg":"都係個句<br />\n開放番莞式Iso 到時保證無港商想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}